text: Experience the epitome of waterfront living with the luxury of mooring your boat right in your backyard, courtesy of your very own double-sided 50' dock! Located in the delightful marine community of Skyline, find this wonderful rambler offering glistening views of the channel & breathtaking sunsets! Enter to discover an expansive, bright, open design, w/vaulted cedar ceilings. Brilliantly refreshed modern kitchen provides an abundance of storage, stainless & elegant quartz crowned w/glass tile splash. Superb primary presents a sitting/office area, center fireplace, spacious walk-in & ensuite bath. 2nd primary w/private full bath, plus additional guest bdrm. Entertain w/ease on the extensive patio, enjoy gardens & all waterfront activities!

Rare opportunity for 5+ usable acres with a 3-bedroom, 2-bath house nestled in the North Cascade Mountains, known as the American Alps. This is any homesteader's dream with rich soil, garden space, a goat pen, chicken coop and plenty of sun. Beautiful mountain views, seasonal creeks, and quick access to some of the best fishing, hiking and climbing in the world. Newer roof. Spacious garage/shop with bonus room above. Expansive deck. Five minutes to the up and coming town of Marblemount, the gateway to the North Cascade National Park, and the wild and scenic Skagit River. A must-see for any outdoor enthusiast!

This meticulously maintained 4-bedroom home with open concept living offers lovely easterly views of Sauk Mtn & valley below, arguably the best in the neighborhood! The home has many recent updates including fresh paint, roof, plush carpet, hot water tank, appliances & walk-in shower off the primary bedroom. Kitchen opens to deck to enjoy sunny afternoons within the nicely landscaped, fenced backyard. Large two car garage offers plenty of covered parking & storage space for all your needs. Conveniently located across from playground on a quiet cul-de-sac. Close to all amenities with easy access for any commute. Do not miss lovely turn key home with all it has to offer.

Pride of ownership shines in this Mount Vernon rambler! This spacious, well-built home is turn-key/move in ready! Featuring an updated kitchen with ample counter space and an attached informal living area. Enjoy the gorgeous traditional living room with a classic wood-burning fireplace and built-in shelving. The large primary bedroom features an attached bath, complemented by two additional main floor bedrooms and a full bath, plus an upper-level bedroom and bath. A dedicated craft room, outdoor shed, two-car garage, fenced backyard, large patio, and beautiful low-maintenance landscaping complete this charming property.

Rare 100-foot waterfront lot on Guemes Islands historic North Beach, framed by views of the B.C. Coastal range, Lummi, Vendovi, & Jack Islands, & Mt. Baker. Once the site of a 1930s cabin, this treasure has been in one family since the 1950s. You have it all here. Historic boat house on grassy lawn next to no-bank, prime sandy beach. Easy stairs to the medium bank building site where a 2011 Residence trailer (w/bells & whistles) is yours while planning your dreams. A tiny 1930s garage has studio written all over it. Staggering views: Northern Lights, meteor showers, harvest moons, glowing sunsets. Dungeness crabbing, clamming, sandcastles on your shared tide flats, great afternoon swimming. Paddle-board, kayak, row, go sailing!
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Sweeping views of the Olympic Mountains, Burrows Island, Allan Island, and Burrows Bay! Almost 3 and a half acres; neighboring parcel to the north also for sale. Imagine enjoying sunsets from the comfort of your home. Privacy while still less than 10 minutes to Skyline Marina and the city of Anacortes. Rural Intermediate zoning, critical areas study and driveway plans available. City of Anacortes water in the street, power in the street, septic site evaluation done and available upon request. Keep the madrona and Douglas fir and cedar trees or clear some of them to open the view further. Mutually agreed upon road agreement must be recorded prior to closing. Schedule a showing today!

This light and bright rambler is full of surprises! Including a new kitchen, high ceilings, skylights, walk-in pantry and studio for your creative side. Large master with private access deck in this park-like setting with mature landscaping. The deck is being prepped for re-finishing. Shelter Bay offers, Marina, Golf Course, Tennis Courts, Pools, Beach Access and Boat Launch.
Single story, 2 bedroom, 1 bath home. Excellent for investors or anyone looking to gain some sweat equity! Great location, close to dining, schools and the hospital.

Experience coastal luxury in this stunning waterfront residence nestled in Shelter Bay. Boasting a 40-foot dock, this home offers unparalleled access to the serene waters that surround it. Open concept living & dining plus a gourmet kitchen equipped w/high end appliances & designed for both functionality and style. Stunning primary bedroom w/charming fireplace & thoughtfully designed sitting area. The ensuite bath is a spa-like haven, with a lavish soaking tub. Whether you're enjoying the panoramic views from the dock or immersing yourself in the luxury of the well-appointed interiors, this Shelter Bay gem promises a lifestyle of tranquility and refinement. Leased land - amenities include clubhouse, sports courts, beach access & more.

Step Back in Time with a Modern Farm House Twist in YOUR Revamped 1925 HOME! Conveniently located in a meticulously maintained neighborhood! YOUR Home Boasts 2 Cozy Bedrooms , Jack and Jill Bath, a Bounty of Fruit Trees to Satisfy Your Sweet Tooth and a Peaceful Garden Escape! Mini Split for your Year-Round Comfort, and a Spacious Corner Lot Ready for Your Creative Touch & Begging for that dreamy detached Garage or workshop - Your Happily-Ever-After HOME Awaits, uncover the Magic of Urban Living in Style! WELCOME HOME!

Welcome to your dream home. On just over an acre of land, this single-level gem boasts territorial views of adjoining farmland. Updated kitchen featuring granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. Natural light pours in through two skylights. Cozy up by one of the two wood fireplaces or the gas freestanding stove. A/C for warm summer days. Beautiful mature landscaping with sprinkler system. Entertain guests on the covered patio overlooking the serene landscape. With an attached two-car garage and a detached heated garage/workshop, there's plenty of space for toys. Utility room with 1/2 bath off of garage. Home is in excellent condition and has been lovingly maintained by the same family since it was built. First time on market!

Prime location 3 Bed 1.5 Bath townhouse nestled into a Mount Vernon cul de sac! Wonderful opportunity for first time home buyers or condo alternative right across Skagit Valley Playfields and College. This 2003 built townhouse has been recently updated with new appliances. Main floor features one bedroom and half bath + primary and third bedroom are on the second floor. Spacious fenced yard, deck + outbuilding for storage. Sit back and relax in the backyard with open mountain view! Excellent walkability!

Got a Plan? Need a flat, Commercial Building lot? Lots of potential uses. Large 18, 000SF corner lot. Corners flagged and lot surveyed. Just a few minutes east of I-5 and close to everything in Mt. Vernon.

Step into serenity with this stunning 2 bed, 2.5 bath retreat overlooking picturesque Big Lake. Newly remodeled from top to bottom, revel in luxury with a brand-new kitchen, bathrooms, and flooring throughout. Enjoy captivating lake views from the expansive upper deck or unwind in the hot tub on the covered lower deck. With a terraced lawn for easy upkeep and a spacious attached workshop/storage area, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Don't miss your chance to experience fully-indulged tranquil living at its finest!

Old-world charm meets modern design! Fully remastered 1900s craftsman w/ superior detail trim & finish work. Everything you need is on the MAIN FLOOR. 2 bdrms, 2 full bthrms PLUS a large finished BONUS area upstairs w/ a half bthrm. Spacious primary bdrm w/ 3 closets & a 5-piece en-suite. Tile floors, walk-in shower w/tile surround plus a tub & linen nook. Open floor concept. Kitchen w/ shaker cabinets, granite ctps, SS applcs, 5 burner gas cooktop & DBL oven. Dining area w/ 9ft coffered ceilings. Living rm w/ cozy gas fireplace & tons of natural light. Leaded glass French doors open to the custom-built deck & fully fenced yard. Oversized 2 car garage/shop & RV/boat parking. NO HOA. Cul-de-sac, easy access to HWY 20 & downtown Anacortes.

Bring your vision to this expansive rambler featuring a fully finished daylight basement. Enjoy a formal dining room, a bright kitchen that opens onto a recently installed Trex deck, great room w/ tons of natural light from its southern exposure, offering views across the spacious 1/2ac lot adorned w/ fruit trees, berries, & ample open space. The 2 full baths have granite counters, radiant heat & tiled floors. Upstairs find the main bed along w/ two add'l beds. Downstairs, discover a generously sized bonus room, family room, 4th bedroom, a large laundry room, 800sf garage w/ 2nd set of WD hook ups, & a mechanical room offering more storage options. RV parking also available. New roof in 2018 w/ lifetime warranty & April Air Purifier system.

Stunning Lake Cavanaugh log home with 120' of lakefront and panoramic views of the islands and glaciers. This home offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort & natural beauty. Newly rebuilt dock with boat lift. Kitchen with walk-pantry, new propane cooktop/oven/fan. Living room has huge rock fireplace, french doors that open to party size deck for entertaining. Main floor primary with newly added 3/4 bath, remodeled 3/4 bath to accommodate guests. Upper level has 2 fully furnished rooms that offer versatility as extra sleeping, office, game room. Lower level has second bedroom with full bath, large rec room with sleeping space, more storage and 600+ bottle wine cellar. Furnished and move in ready for the summer. Detached 1 car garage.

Escape to panoramic vistas of Burrows Bay and surrounding islands from this modern sanctuary. Step into an open concept living space adorned with a towering fireplace, seamlessly blending with a gourmet kitchen boasting a central cooking island and gas range. Your serene haven offers a main-level primary suite with a lavish ensuite, featuring a soaking tub & tiled shower. Descend to a lower-level retreat or possible MIL suite, complete with a cozy rec room, kitchenette, bedrooms & bath. Outside, delight in landscaped gardens, a covered deck, & side patio, perfect for soaking in the scenery. 4 car garage for all of your toys & storage. Enjoy the Skyline amenities, including a marina & beach access, embracing a lifestyle of coastal luxury.

Welcome to SummerSun Estates. Built in 2018, this impeccable 4-bdm, 2.5-bth home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort & privacy, nestled at the end of a serene street, bordering a lush green belt & walking trail. The spacious kitchen features granite countertops, newer dishwasher/micro, ample storage, eating bar, & pantry area. The large open living space flows into dining area, leading to private backyard & patio. Imagine relaxing in the hot tub under the gazebo, surrounded by nature's beauty. Upstairs, you'll find an extra wide hallway, washer/dryer, three bedrooms w/full bathroom, along w/primary bedroom boasting a en-suite bathroom & walk-in closet. And a private office at the entry. Built w/a sprinkler system. A must see home!

A home and property you have been waiting for with features you will love! Just outside of town on a private lane you will be greeted by big, tall trees will lead you to this home. A large driveway opens up to this beautiful home and shop. The property is very private and gets lots of sunshine. This well-kept home features 1712 sq ft of total living space, formal living and dining rooms, family room with fireplace off the kitchen, 3 bd and 2 full baths. Large covered concrete patio to enjoy off kitchen. Enjoy a fantastic view of the property from every room. The detached shop is 30x36, over 1080 sq ft of open area with built in work area.

Welcome to this wonderful split-level home in the Thunderbird neighborhood on a huge 16, 117 square foot lot. This home is 2, 256 square feet, 4 bedrooms, one full bathroom and two 3/4 bathrooms. Many features have been updated like the granite countertops, custom pullouts throughout the kitchen, Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout all of the common areas, newer furnace with air conditioning, natural gas fireplaces on each floor and a custom ADA style shower on the lower floor with lots of grab bars. The fully fenced backyard is relaxing oasis with a waterfall, custom trails, huge rear deck, and beautiful landscaping.

Welcome to your new home in Mount Vernon, WA! This cozy 2 bedroom, 1 bath manufactured home features new carpet and fresh paint throughout, giving it a modern and inviting feel. With the opportunity to own your own home and the convenience of space rent, this home offers a unique living experience. Plus, water, sewer, and garbage are included in the space rent, making budgeting a breeze. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this home your own!

Spacious tasteful two story home has major updates including new roof, quality flooring throughout, interior paint, and furnace/heat pump providing air conditioning for hot summer days. Main floor features walk-in pantry off kitchen open to stylish dining room, big living room with lots of natural light, and den/office overlooking the scenic yard. Backyard is fully fenced with patio to enjoy those barbeques and relaxing. Upstairs leads to a great bonus room with a 2nd living/family area open to an alcove to use for play/computer stations/crafting. King size master bedroom has ensuite bath with soaking tub, and large walk-in closet with new upscale closet organizer. All 3 bathrooms have been updated. Close to shopping, restaurants & freeway.

Sweeping views of the Olympic Mountains, Burrows Island, Allan Island, and Burrows Bay! Almost 3 and a half acres; neighboring parcel to the south also for sale. Imagine enjoying sunsets from the comfort of your home. Privacy while still less than 10 minutes to Skyline Marina and the city of Anacortes. Rural Intermediate zoning, critical areas study and driveway plans available. City of Anacortes water in the street, power in the street, septic site evaluation done and available upon request. Keep the madrona and Douglas fir and cedar trees or clear some of them to open the view further. Mutually agreed upon road agreement must be recorded prior to closing. Schedule a showing today!

Escape to your own private oasis on the Skagit River! This stunning 1.5 Acre park-like property is perched on a high bank, safely out of the flood zone. Enjoy the peace and tranquility as you relax and unwind in this beautiful natural setting. This land comes with a spacious shop, ample storage and workspace with all of the additional outbuildings. Large, well maintained fenced garden to keep out all the friendly animal neighbors. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a slice of paradise perfect for your vacation retreat.

Nestled on a large lot, this gem boasts a greenbelt backdrop, perfect for nature lovers. The fenced backyard invites relaxation with a built-in firepit area and a terraced patio, ideal for entertaining under the stars. As you step inside, be greeted by a grand double door and a dining room adorned with a soaring two-story ceiling, creating a dramatic ambiance. The eat-in kitchen seamlessly connects to the cozy living room, fostering a warm & inviting atmosphere for gatherings. Your sanctuary awaits in the primary bedroom, featuring an ensuite with a luxurious soaking tub, separate shower, & a spacious walk-in closet. Enjoy a spacious 3-car garage with plenty of room for all of your toys or a add a workshop. Must see and won't last long!

This charming 2-bedroom rambler bordering a huge greenspace features vaulted ceilings, a large open living and dining area with hardwood floors, some new appliances, and onsite laundry. The home, built in 2003 and remodeled in 2016, boasts energy-efficient features including R38 ceilings, R30 floors, and R15 walls, ensuring comfort and affordability. Enjoy community events and natural beauty in Mount Vernon, including the vibrant Farmers Market, Skagit Valley Tulip Festival, and Skagit County Fair. Close to town, parks, and Skagit Valley College, this home is perfect as a starter or rental property with scenic views of the Cascade foothills.

Bayview Ridge Rambler on 1 acre! Three bedrooms, two bathrooms, 2073 sq. ft., separate room off of entrance, living room w/vaulted ceiling, dining area & kitchen open to the living room. Gas range carpet 1 yr. Cozy space off of laundry room would make a small off/sewing area. Spacious bedrooms, primary with separate tub & shower. Three car garage (752 sq. ft.) attached. So much potential to bring your touches & make this home shine. The lot is level & cleared, lots of room to build a shop or park an RV. Great location, walk to school, (Bayview K-8th), convenient to I-5 & out of flood plain.

Welcome to Garden Meadows in Sedro Woolley! A 2-story open concept home w/ 4 bedrooms, office & 2.5 baths. You'll love the LVP flooring & natural gas fireplace. The kitchen features quartz countertops, large pantry, & GE appliances. W/ 7 mini-split ductless heating & cooling systems, you can enjoy a perfect temperature year round. Upstairs is 4 bedrms. including a primary suite. 3 more bedrms. Full guest bath & bonus rm. Laundry rm. conveniently located near bedrms. This home, built in 2021, offers all the modern amenities & finishes you desire. A two-car garage w/ epoxy floor, provides a sleek & clean storage space. A fully fenced backyard & patio, for private outdoor living. Sedro Woolley is located near camping, hiking, skiing & more !

COVERED 36 foot long by 14.5 foot wide boat slip in Skyline Marina with secured gate access. With water and electricity at the slip. Just minutes from downtown Anacortes. Skyline Marina is the gateway to San Juan Islands with the shortest run into the islands of any marina. You will find restrooms, showers, laundry facilities, groceries, ice and ample parking. Sold as-is.
